  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Hot Dragon Chili Salad</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p>The <b>Hot Dragon Chili Salad</b> is a <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Warly\" title=\"Warly\">Warly</a> specific <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">item</a> cooked in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Crock_Pot\" title=\"Portable Crock Pot\">Portable Crock Pot</a> by combining one <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dragon_Fruit\" title=\"Dragon Fruit\">Dragon Fruit</a>, one <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pepper\" title=\"Pepper\">Pepper</a>, and two fillers.\n</p><p>Using two <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twigs</a> as filler will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dragon_Pie\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragon Pie\">Dragon Pie</a> while using meat will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meatballs\" title=\"Meatballs\">Meatballs</a>. Attempting to cook a Hot Dragon Chili Salad in a regular <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> will result in Dragon Pie.\n</p><p>Consuming a Hot Dragon Chili Salad keeps player temperature up to 40° above ambient temperature for 5 minutes. It does not make player immune to <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Freezing\" title=\"Freezing\">freezing</a> effects from the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Deerclops\" title=\"Deerclops\">Deerclops</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blue_Hound\" title=\"Blue Hound\">Blue Hounds</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Staff\" title=\"Ice Staff\">Ice Staffs</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dragon_Fruits\" title=\"Dragon Fruits\"><img alt=\"Dragon Fruits.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dragon_Fruits.png?713df4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Peppers\" title=\"Peppers\"><img alt=\"Peppers.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Peppers.png?a94896\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Crock_Pot\" title=\"Portable Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Portable Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Portable_Crock_Pot.png/42px-Portable_Crock_Pot.png?f4c0d3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hot_Dragon_Chili_Salad\" title=\"Hot Dragon Chili Salad\"><img alt=\"Hot Dragon Chili Salad.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Hot_Dragon_Chili_Salad.png?daeff0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>Fillers cannot be <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\">Eggs</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Inedibles\" title=\"Inedibles\">Inedibles</a>.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dragon_Fruits\" title=\"Dragon Fruits\"><img alt=\"Dragon Fruits.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dragon_Fruits.png?713df4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Peppers\" title=\"Peppers\"><img alt=\"Peppers.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Peppers.png?a94896\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Crock_Pot\" title=\"Portable Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Portable Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Portable_Crock_Pot.png/42px-Portable_Crock_Pot.png?f4c0d3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hot_Dragon_Chili_Salad\" title=\"Hot Dragon Chili Salad\"><img alt=\"Hot Dragon Chili Salad.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Hot_Dragon_Chili_Salad.png?daeff0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dragon_Fruits\" title=\"Dragon Fruits\"><img alt=\"Dragon Fruits.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dragon_Fruits.png?713df4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"ht