  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Salad Ớt Rồng Nóng là một món ăn đặc biệt của Don&#x27;t Starve Together và Warly được nấu trong Nồi Hầm Di Động bằng cách kết hợp một Thanh Long, một Tiêu và hai chất độn.</p>",
  "title": "Hot Dragon Chili Salad",
  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|foodRecipe ={{Pic|32px|Dragon Fruits}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Peppers}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x2\n|foodPortableCrockPot = 1\n|canBeBurned=1\n|foodType = [[Veggie]] [[File:Veggie.png|32px|]]\n|icon = {{FULLPAGENAME}}.png\n|image = {{FULLPAGENAME}} Dropped.png\n|hpRestored = -3\n|hungerRestored = 25\n|sanityRestored = 10\n|cooktime = 15 sec\n|priority = 30\n|spoil = 15 Days\n|stack = 40\n|perk = Increases temperature by 40 degrees for 5 minutes.\n|spawnCode = \"dragonchilisalad\"\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = I hope I can handle the spice level.\n|willow = I can't wait to eat it.\n|wolfgang = Vegetables help Wolfgang grow big and strong.\n|wendy = I missed having someone make me dinner...\n|wx78 = MY MINIONS WILL SUSTAIN ME\n|wickerbottom = I do like fresh greens.\n|woodie = Looks really good, buddy.\n|maxwell = I permit him to stay so long as he keeps cooking.\n|wigfrid = Yeuch! I was prömised a feast!\n|webber = Okay, we'll eat a salad.\n|winona = Can't believe Warly's got me eatin' salads.\n|warly = A hint of spice to awaken the tastebuds.\n|wortox = Warly spends a lot of time on this stuff.\n|wormwood = Eating bits\n|wurt = Mmmm, thank you fancy cook man!\n|walter = Is it made from real dragons?\n|wanda = Warly always finds such unique combinations.\n|choose = warly\n}}\nThe '''Hot Dragon Chili Salad''' is a ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'' and [[Warly]] specific [[Food]] [[item]] cooked in the [[Portable Crock Pot]] by combining one [[Dragon Fruit]], one [[Pepper]], and two fillers.\n\nUsing two [[Twigs]] as filler will result in [[Dragon Pie]] while using meat will result in [[Meatballs]]. Attempting to cook a Hot Dragon Chili Salad in a regular [[Crock Pot]] will result in Dragon Pie.\n\nConsuming a Hot Dragon Chili Salad keeps player temperature up to 40° above ambient temperature for 5 minutes. It does not make player immune to [[freezing]] effects from the [[Deerclops|Deerclops]], [[Blue Hound|Blue Hounds]] or [[Ice Staff|Ice Staffs]]. \n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Dragon Fruits\n|item2 = Peppers\n|item3 = Filler\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Hot Dragon Chili Salad\n|note = Fillers cannot be [[Meats]], [[Eggs]] or [[Inedibles]].\n}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Dragon Fruits\n|item2 = Peppers\n|item3 = Ice\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Hot Dragon Chili Salad\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Dragon Fruits\n|item2 = Peppers\n|item3 = Berry\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Hot Dragon Chili Salad\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Dragon Fruits\n|item2 = Peppers\n|item3 = Ripe Stone Fruit\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Hot Dragon Chili Salad\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Dragon Fruits\n|item2 = Peppers\n|item3 = Kelp Fronds\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Hot Dragon Chili Salad\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Dragon Fruits\n|item2 = Peppers\n|count2 = 3\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Hot Dragon Chili Salad\n}}\n{{clear}}\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nHot Dragon Chili Salad 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\n</gallery>\n{{Edible Items}}\n[[Category:Portable Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]\n[[Category:Health Loss]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Warmth]]\n[[zh:辣龙椒沙拉]]"
}
